<div id="feedback-modal" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-header" style="background-color: #a73d3b  ">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
    <h3 id="myModalLabel" style="color:white">Congratulazioni <%= current_user.username %>!</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body center" style="background-color: #b94a48; color:white; padding-top: 40px">
    <p>Hai completato tutti gli esercizi del training program : <b><%= @done_program.title %></b>, Saremo lieti se lasciassi un commento con i tuoi pareri su questo programma di allenamento </p>
    <br />
    <b>RATING</b>
    <br />
    <span class="rating">
      <span class="star"></span>
      <span class="star"></span>
      <span class="star"></span>
      <span class="star"></span>
      <span class="star"></span>
    </span>
    <br />
    <br />
    <%= form_for :feedback do |f| %>
    <%= f.text_area :body, :placeholder => "Il Tuo Commento ...", rows: 5 %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <button class="btn btn-success btn-large"><i class="icon-envelope"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Give feeds</button>
    <button class="btn btn-large" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true"><i class="icon-reply"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Indietro</button>
  </div>
</div>
